sub_title: Health and Social Psychology Master Student
summary:
Master student, specializing in Health and Social Psychology at Maastricht University, Netherlands. 
I completed my Bachelor's degree in Biopsychology at UP Famnit, Slovenia. My thesis was titled Animal - assisted therapy as a preventive measure for suicidal behavior in youth.

My main areas of interest are Human-Animal Interactions, Animal-Assisted Therapy, Suicidality and Self-harm.
